: 1726765200, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1577304799798124"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "6328319427296847", "version": "3.9"}, "id": "2498639197047980", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": false, "primary_binaries": {"nodes": [{"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "2436897736439055", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "6328319427296847"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "2498639197047980"}]}, "change_log": "v.0.93.7.1", "created_date": 1691413741, "id": "6328319427296847", "version": "3.9", "version_code": 165, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": {"id": "6328285023966954"}, "asset_files": {"count": 12}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "2436897736439055", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "6328319427296847"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": []}, "change_log": null, "created_date": 1691404011, "id": "6327940207334769", "version": "3.9", "version_code": 164, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": {"id": "6327915787337211"}, "asset_files": {"count": 12}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "2436897736439055", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "6328319427296847"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "2498639197047980"}]}, "change_log": "v.0.93.7.0\nSignificantly changed the hand animation and head-shaking effect.\nSignificantly decreased the overall boost speed of sprint and slide.\nAddressed an animation dragging issue for grabbing magazines.\nAddressed miscellaneous issues that could cause errors in mods.\nAddressed the bug that hinders the keyboard from being displayed during the match in the Social section.\nAddress the issue that would cause the irregular UI shaking.\nAddressed miscellaneous issues caused by slide.\nFixed the incorrect Stabilizer performance.\nFixed the invisible teammate walkie-talkie issue.\nFixed the missing texture glitches on various weapons.\nFixed the texture issue of bullets in the chamber.", "created_date": 1691244706, "id": "6322568477871942", "version": "3.9", "version_code": 163, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": {"id": "6322538411208282"}, "asset_files": {"count": 12}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "2436897736439055", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "6328319427296847"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": []}, "change_log": null, "created_date": 1691239265, "id": "6322340104561446", "version": "3.9", "version_code": 162, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": {"id": "6322306727898117"}, "asset_files": {"count": 12}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "2436897736439055", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "6328319427296847"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "2498639197047980"}]}, "change_log": "v.0.93.6.0\nAdded\nAdded new hand animation while sprinting\nAdded speaker icon on the scoreboard, now players can see the player who is speaking directly.\nAdded a 2-second respawn protection.\nAdded a new stabilizer for all weapons with high scopes.\nAdded a new 'Favorite' button for the mod section.\nAdded new scope options for ASVAL/UMP45/Vector/MP5.\nChanged\nMute-all will now be in effect persistent through lobby/matches if not leaving the current lobby/match.\nOptimized the performance on slope terrains and slide speed on all surfaces.\nOverhauled reticle patterns for all high scopes.\nSignificantly reduced weapon shaking while using high scopes.\nSignificantly reduced the recoil of all pistols.\nReduced the shot spread of all shotguns by 20%.\nIncreased the shotgun damage across the board. Damage at 10 meters has been increased by 20%, 10-20 meters increased by 25%, and 20-30 meters increased by 50%.\nThe horizontal recoil of AKM/AK74/FAL/AUG/FAMAS was reduced by 50%.\nReduced the vertical recoil of FAL by 15%\nReduced the horizontal recoil of MP7 and MP5A3 by 30%.\nIncreased the muzzle recovery speed of Deagle and Magnum by 40%\nDecreased the base damage of CZ805 from 31 to 29.\nTactical reload moves now can be performed with SVD/QBZ 95/As VAL/FAL.\nMagazine releases now can be performed with MP7.\nOptimized the reload experience of P90/Vector/Magnum.\nOptimized the tactical reload experience.\nOptimized firing selector position for various weapons.\nOptimized the scope position of SKS/ASVAL/Magnum.\nOptimized the model for Aimpoint T1 Scope for SMGs.\nOptimized the firing speed, recoil, model, and animation for Bren/M1941/M1 Garand.\nFixed\nFixed a bug in Bomb Defusal that the bomb can be planted with a knife.\nFixed a bug that players can pick up props and guns after being eliminated.\nFixed a bug that grenades could float in the air after the player is eliminated.\nFixed a bug that claymore can be triggered by grenade explosion on the other side of the obstacle.\nFixed a bug that ASVAL can reload with AK74u magazine.\nRemoved the incorrect firing mode of M3A1 and MP40.\nPotentially addressed the ADS tweaking issue.\nPotentially addressed a game crashing issue triggered by device memory restriction.\nPotentially addressed a game crashing issue triggered by overloading mods.\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n", "created_date": 1690989348, "id": "6313158462146277", "version": "3.9", "version_code": 161, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": {"id": "6313120428816747"}, "asset_files": {"count": 12}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}]}}, "viewer": {"user": null}}}